{"tid":2177831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係到屌手足唔小心比支共捉既軍師 你地有冇惗過佢地係咩心情？","createTime":"2020-08-28T04:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T05:37:32.000Z","uid":41389,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a97346e20972480ffbdba9b7a08f1a191a91db9c","tid":2177831,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T04:02:05.000Z","msg":"係香港等死 比紅官入罪判十幾年<br />\n辛苦夾幾十萬準備坐大飛走<br />\n要3日3夜先到台灣 途中風吹雨打<br />\n行到一半 比支共海軍截住<br />\n拎槍指住你立即送中既心情<br />\n你班淨係識屌呢樣屌個樣既人唔會明架啦<br />\n我屌你老母啦 日屌夜屌 <br />\n黃圈又比你屌散 手足又比你屌到死曬心啦<br />\n咁撚叻你地又咪係留係到比人強姦做港豬<br />\n唔好落井下石好無？<br />\n<br />\nPS 只希望佢地可以返番黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfade1e33d39c635e4d03bc1760b4789e8716f0b","tid":2177831,"uid":41389,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T04:02:58.000Z","msg":"唔排除亦有五毛帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c55a0a54866e49f0beb4d570ee43d405200baf6","tid":2177831,"uid":41389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T04:03:26.000Z","msg":"手足要平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ef7768ce2fb2dff97c42a636b9c93ff21f3e14","tid":2177831,"uid":221211,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T04:03:35.000Z","msg":"惡意留言唔好咁上心 分分鐘係 PR 5毛狗"},{"pid":"b5050a36db8945f6a4a901a6f2cab3e4af0c9695","tid":2177831,"uid":41389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"38ef7768ce2fb2dff97c42a636b9c93ff21f3e14","tid":2177831,"uid":221211,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T04:03:35.000Z","msg":"惡意留言唔好咁上心 分分鐘係 PR 5毛狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T04:04:38.000Z","msg":"但有班傻仔真係比佢地帶到風向"},{"pid":"b282d6128405c11903e9fc1b54160ff2391f6c09","tid":2177831,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38ef7768ce2fb2dff97c42a636b9c93ff21f3e14","tid":2177831,"uid":221211,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T04:03:3